title: Ten Big Predictions for Draft Night | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Robert Mays and Danny Kelly huddle up to discuss who will be selected first, how the defensive linemen will shake out, if any linebackers or tight ends will be in the top 10, and more.

Hosts: Robert Mays and Danny Kelly
